WEBVTT

01:52.350 --> 01:57.530
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.680 --> 02:01.940
[Episode 30]

02:23.870 --> 02:24.710
Grandfather.

02:28.440 --> 02:29.630
Is the Governor

02:30.400 --> 02:33.329
going to shoot down
the Zheng family's Raven Legion?

02:34.340 --> 02:36.210
No blood can be shed
on the ceremonial review's grounds.

02:36.210 --> 02:37.210
This is the rule.

02:38.200 --> 02:40.150
As long as Zheng Tao
dares to release his ravens,

02:40.150 --> 02:42.660
we will shoot
every single one of them down.

02:44.140 --> 02:45.140
Absolutely not.

02:45.570 --> 02:48.079
Even if we can
shoot down all those ravens,

02:48.110 --> 02:50.760
no blood can be shed
on the ceremonial review's grounds.

02:50.760 --> 02:52.620
Moreover, if we killed the ravens

02:52.880 --> 02:54.670
and the Zheng family

02:54.700 --> 02:55.860
held it against us,

02:56.280 --> 02:58.630
wouldn't we be penny wise
and pound foolish?

02:58.630 --> 02:59.560
Fan Yun is right.

03:00.470 --> 03:02.730
If we shot down
the ravens of Zheng's Army,

03:02.730 --> 03:04.930
the consequences would be disastrous.

03:04.960 --> 03:05.960
We saw those ravens

03:05.960 --> 03:08.030
seemed to be trained
to only attack Qi's Army.

03:08.030 --> 03:10.750
Why don't we have
Qi's Army change their uniforms?

03:10.750 --> 03:11.840
That's even worse.

03:12.390 --> 03:13.690
The uniforms of Qi's Army

03:13.690 --> 03:15.880
represent the face of the Qi family.

03:16.280 --> 03:18.010
If we win by changing uniforms,

03:18.030 --> 03:19.690
it would be an unfair victory.

03:21.910 --> 03:23.280
Actually,

03:23.630 --> 03:24.890
I do have an idea

03:25.120 --> 03:26.120
that we could try.

03:28.960 --> 03:30.890
What idea do you have, Lady Fan Yun?

03:31.810 --> 03:34.010
Your Excellency, do you still remember

03:34.400 --> 03:35.730
that night in Yong City?

04:49.930 --> 04:51.370
I keep my word.

04:52.070 --> 04:53.420
How could I forget

04:53.970 --> 04:55.570
what I promised Mayor Zheng?

05:01.310 --> 05:03.000
Today, I witnessed

05:03.000 --> 05:05.070
the Governor's great vision.

05:05.390 --> 05:06.750
It's a worthwhile trip.

05:08.600 --> 05:10.630
The Governor is wise and brilliant.

05:13.720 --> 05:14.630
In this competition,

05:14.630 --> 05:17.160
I, Zheng, accept my defeat.

05:19.270 --> 05:20.630
Today also let me witness

05:20.630 --> 05:22.830
the extraordinary strength
of Zheng's Army.

05:22.830 --> 05:25.310
With such an army
stationed in Jing City,

05:25.800 --> 05:27.530
how could I not feel reassured?

05:33.040 --> 05:35.440
Thank you for your trust, Your Excellency.

05:55.050 --> 05:56.520
Get out of the way!

05:58.800 --> 05:59.630
Wei Ying!

06:00.160 --> 06:01.120
Wei Ying!

06:27.720 --> 06:29.770
How are Commander Wei's injuries?

06:31.630 --> 06:32.470
Three arrows.

06:33.920 --> 06:36.650
Each one was shot
from an extremely tricky angle,

06:36.940 --> 06:39.140
all aimed at Commander Wei's vitals.

06:40.020 --> 06:41.820
His life isn't in danger, right?

06:42.300 --> 06:43.540
I certainly hope not.

06:44.840 --> 06:45.810
I'm just afraid

06:47.520 --> 06:49.780
someone else doesn't think the same way.

06:53.870 --> 06:54.870
Your Excellency,

06:55.830 --> 06:58.270
do you think I did this?

06:58.950 --> 07:01.040
The three arrows all came from Jing City.

07:01.040 --> 07:02.560
How do you explain that?

07:04.360 --> 07:06.920
Could it be that you performed poorly
in the review,

07:06.920 --> 07:08.180
and you're dissatisfied,

07:08.180 --> 07:10.580
so you did this foolish act
in a fit of anger?

07:12.480 --> 07:13.600
Zheng's Army

07:14.070 --> 07:15.160
has strict discipline

07:15.160 --> 07:16.360
and is well-trained.

07:16.680 --> 07:18.800
Would we publicly retaliate

07:19.040 --> 07:20.520
just because our formation was broken?

07:20.520 --> 07:22.250
If this excuse spread,

07:22.690 --> 07:24.220
wouldn't it be ridiculous?

07:26.430 --> 07:27.240
Mayor Zheng,

07:28.000 --> 07:29.240
even if your rhetoric

07:29.750 --> 07:31.360
can convince me now,

07:31.870 --> 07:33.930
I'm afraid it won't convince others.

07:34.190 --> 07:34.860
Who else?

07:35.909 --> 07:36.590
Me!

07:45.470 --> 07:47.450
The wound is half an inch from the heart.

07:47.450 --> 07:48.870
If my brother hadn't dodged in time,

07:48.870 --> 07:49.790
that arrow

07:49.950 --> 07:51.409
would have taken his life.

07:54.010 --> 07:55.420
How exactly does your Zheng family

07:55.420 --> 07:56.909
train your soldiers?

07:56.940 --> 07:58.430
They are just a disorganized mess.

07:58.430 --> 07:59.480
Not only do they have clumsy formations,

07:59.480 --> 08:00.560
but they also have poor character.

08:00.560 --> 08:01.560
A bunch of sore losers,

08:01.560 --> 08:02.680
they aren't even as well-trained

08:02.680 --> 08:04.410
as the Wei family's livestock.

08:05.740 --> 08:06.780
Miss Wei,

08:07.500 --> 08:08.630
don't get agitated.

08:08.970 --> 08:10.030
Let's talk calmly.

08:10.430 --> 08:11.600
That's my own brother.

08:11.600 --> 08:12.830
How can I not be agitated?

08:12.830 --> 08:14.690
This matter
has not been fully investigated yet.

08:14.690 --> 08:16.420
Do not make false accusations.

08:25.350 --> 08:26.150
Grandfather,

08:26.400 --> 08:27.790
the military camp has done a count.

08:27.790 --> 08:29.650
Three arrows are indeed missing.

08:29.980 --> 08:32.340
Speak louder. I can't hear you.

08:33.490 --> 08:35.350
Three arrows are indeed missing.

08:35.669 --> 08:36.360
Tell me,

08:36.630 --> 08:37.630
what should we do?

08:38.950 --> 08:41.610
There must be
something suspicious about this.

08:44.260 --> 08:45.260
Miss Wei.

08:45.910 --> 08:47.080
Give me some time.

08:47.080 --> 08:48.480
Let me find out the truth.

08:48.780 --> 08:49.880
Give you time?

08:50.380 --> 08:52.310
So you can escape back to Jing City?

08:53.440 --> 08:54.320
The members of the Zheng family

08:54.320 --> 08:56.650
never deny our actions or shirk our debts.

08:59.510 --> 09:00.080
Fine.

09:00.370 --> 09:02.370
Then I will write a letter right now.

09:02.790 --> 09:03.960
Dear Father,

09:05.080 --> 09:05.630
my brother

09:05.630 --> 09:07.480
was severely injured while sparring

09:07.480 --> 09:08.270
with Zheng's Army.

09:08.270 --> 09:09.980
His life is in imminent danger.

09:09.980 --> 09:12.160
Mayor Zheng says
it was absolutely not their doing.

09:12.160 --> 09:13.490
We'll give him some time

09:13.500 --> 09:14.790
to find a scapegoat.

09:16.570 --> 09:17.360
Miss Wei,

09:18.240 --> 09:19.200
why are you so stubborn

09:19.200 --> 09:20.600
and won't listen to reason?

09:20.600 --> 09:21.550
If there's no explanation

09:21.550 --> 09:22.800
for today's matter,

09:23.150 --> 09:25.130
you'll be the ones
not listening to reason.

09:25.130 --> 09:25.870
From now on,

09:26.080 --> 09:27.390
don't even think about buying

09:27.390 --> 09:29.590
another bag of salt from the Wei family.

09:30.420 --> 09:32.350
I can't reason with a girl like you.

09:32.680 --> 09:35.010
You don't call the shots
in the Wei family.

09:35.120 --> 09:37.050
Wait until Commander Wei wakes up.

09:37.070 --> 09:38.110
Then we'll talk.

09:42.330 --> 09:43.240
Grandfather,

09:43.270 --> 09:45.830
Miss Wei is deeply favored
by the Master of the Wei family.

09:45.830 --> 09:47.720
She might actually call the shots.

09:47.720 --> 09:49.890
Besides, the Wei family
controls the entire salt vein.

09:49.890 --> 09:51.220
Falling out at this time

09:51.590 --> 09:53.510
might be detrimental to Jing City,

09:53.510 --> 09:54.870
so we'd better not push the Wei family

09:54.870 --> 09:56.440
to become our enemy.

10:03.240 --> 10:04.240
Miss Wei.

10:04.810 --> 10:05.870
In your opinion,

10:06.630 --> 10:08.630
how should this matter be resolved?

10:08.850 --> 10:09.970
As for me,

10:09.990 --> 10:11.110
I am very fair.

10:11.550 --> 10:12.500
An eye for an eye,

10:12.790 --> 10:14.520
three arrows for three arrows.

10:17.870 --> 10:18.870
Even so,

10:19.330 --> 10:21.590
the injuries sustained by Commander Wei

10:21.700 --> 10:23.830
will not be lessened in the slightest.

10:25.270 --> 10:27.750
How about we bring Zheng's Army

10:27.750 --> 10:29.280
to Gao City to do hard labor?

10:31.270 --> 10:34.090
You are taking advantage
of their precarious position.

10:34.090 --> 10:36.350
And you show no respect for Zheng's Army.

10:36.680 --> 10:38.310
Since you say no to everything,

10:38.310 --> 10:40.170
then you make the decision for us.

10:42.430 --> 10:43.360
How about this?

10:44.130 --> 10:47.610
Zheng's Army is weak on the inside
and is easily defeated.

10:47.870 --> 10:49.010
This shows that the commanding officers

10:49.010 --> 10:51.340
are incompetent and fail to do their jobs.

10:51.450 --> 10:52.910
Why not leave Zheng's Army

10:53.190 --> 10:54.590
in Ling'an for a while,

10:54.800 --> 10:57.440
so that Qi's Army can teach them a lesson?

10:58.370 --> 11:00.100
What do you think, Mayor Zheng?

11:02.200 --> 11:02.840
Sure.

11:03.090 --> 11:04.150
It's settled then.

11:12.810 --> 11:14.340
The Zheng family's things.

11:39.920 --> 11:41.430
Look at you.

11:41.550 --> 11:43.280
You almost ruined everything.

11:43.280 --> 11:43.860
Well,

11:44.430 --> 11:45.920
I was nervous.

11:45.940 --> 11:46.660
Besides,

11:46.690 --> 11:47.960
you were standing right there.

11:47.960 --> 11:49.510
What if I missed?

11:49.510 --> 11:50.960
You have the nerve to say that?

11:50.960 --> 11:52.220
If I hadn't thrown myself at it,

11:52.220 --> 11:53.480
you would have missed.

11:56.690 --> 11:57.450
Move!

12:09.560 --> 12:11.190
So you guys planned this all along?

12:11.190 --> 12:12.380
Everyone knew about it,

12:12.380 --> 12:13.300
except me?

12:16.730 --> 12:18.420
It's not that we didn't want to tell you,

12:18.420 --> 12:20.090
but we were afraid that if you knew,

12:20.090 --> 12:21.820
you wouldn't have acted convincingly.

12:21.820 --> 12:22.990
Look at you just now.

12:23.010 --> 12:24.210
You were so imposing.

12:24.460 --> 12:27.060
Weren't you afraid
I'd get mad and attack them?

12:28.100 --> 12:29.440
We believe in you.

12:29.760 --> 12:31.550
Although you look

12:31.630 --> 12:33.110
very impulsive on the outside,

12:33.110 --> 12:34.540
overall,

12:34.560 --> 12:37.160
you're reasonable
and know what's important.

12:39.270 --> 12:41.420
So the main credit today

12:41.440 --> 12:42.320
still goes to

12:42.350 --> 12:44.230
our Miss Wei.

12:44.270 --> 12:45.730
Isn't that right, Gao Ran?

12:46.310 --> 12:46.940
Yes.

12:47.550 --> 12:49.210
Miss Wei played a crucial role

12:49.270 --> 12:51.400
in making Zheng Tao suffer in silence.

12:51.810 --> 12:52.810
Really?

12:54.440 --> 12:55.930
Yeah, I told you.

12:55.950 --> 12:56.630
Leaving such a small thing to me

12:56.630 --> 12:58.400
is no problem at all.

13:00.370 --> 13:01.560
Anyway,

13:01.960 --> 13:02.670
my anxious heart

13:02.670 --> 13:04.070
can finally settle down.

13:05.000 --> 13:06.610
Next, about the gate commander,

13:06.610 --> 13:08.540
we won't be led by the nose anymore.

13:08.740 --> 13:09.980
I don't understand.

13:10.010 --> 13:12.410
What does this have to do
with the gate commander?

13:12.410 --> 13:13.680
Ignoring Zheng Tao at first

13:13.680 --> 13:15.410
and making Zheng's Army suffer

13:15.760 --> 13:17.360
not only broke their spirit,

13:17.390 --> 13:19.310
but also gave us bargaining chips.

13:19.310 --> 13:20.730
When they became unsettled,

13:20.730 --> 13:22.260
we proposed a ceremonial review.

13:22.260 --> 13:24.250
It seemed like we gave
the Zheng family a way out,

13:24.250 --> 13:26.380
but actually, they fell into our trap.

13:27.360 --> 13:28.480
I thought trapping them

13:28.480 --> 13:29.590
and making them have a review

13:29.590 --> 13:31.320
was to show the governor's power

13:31.320 --> 13:32.430
and show them who's the boss

13:32.430 --> 13:33.790
of the Nine Cities.

13:34.270 --> 13:35.200
That was just

13:35.200 --> 13:37.200
a show of strength at the beginning.

13:37.670 --> 13:38.630
So,

13:39.270 --> 13:41.750
letting them review was just a feint.

13:41.750 --> 13:44.680
Making Zheng Tao suffer in silence
was the real move.

13:46.030 --> 13:47.760
Actually, the governor wanted

13:47.870 --> 13:50.750
to keep their people
and soldiers from the start.

13:53.600 --> 13:54.440
This way,

13:54.440 --> 13:55.840
Jing City not only lost its leader,

13:55.840 --> 13:57.120
but also lost 20,000 elite soldiers.

13:57.120 --> 13:58.800
If I were Zheng Tao, I'd want to die.

13:58.800 --> 14:00.800
Your Excellency, you are ruthless.

14:01.600 --> 14:03.510
Next, about the gate commander...

14:03.510 --> 14:04.470
Our main goal

14:04.960 --> 14:07.270
is to crush Zheng Tao's ambition
to secede.

14:07.270 --> 14:09.360
As for the younger generation
of the Zheng family,

14:09.360 --> 14:11.120
we will divide and conquer them,

14:11.120 --> 14:12.580
defeating them one by one.

14:13.360 --> 14:14.350
Then,

14:14.520 --> 14:16.300
regarding the candidate
for Jing City's gate commander,

14:16.300 --> 14:17.300
Your Excellency,

14:17.750 --> 14:18.880
what are your plans?

14:20.910 --> 14:21.650
Well...

14:22.870 --> 14:24.070
Let me think about it.

14:26.280 --> 14:29.830
Playing dumb and advancing step by step,

14:30.500 --> 14:32.440
luring us into a trap,

14:33.100 --> 14:34.500
they checkmated us,

14:34.530 --> 14:36.530
leaving us with nothing to say.

14:37.270 --> 14:40.440
This time, I have truly lost

14:40.440 --> 14:42.180
both face and substance.

14:45.120 --> 14:46.790
Is this the same person

14:46.790 --> 14:48.190
as the rumored Governor?

14:55.120 --> 14:56.490
Fighting without breaking bonds,

14:56.490 --> 15:00.850
he really got some of
Eldest Brother's true teachings.

15:02.510 --> 15:03.870
He didn't dare to completely fall out

15:03.870 --> 15:05.790
for fear of forcing
the Zheng family to rebel,

15:05.790 --> 15:08.510
causing turmoil in the world.

15:08.750 --> 15:11.080
Eldest Brother
was convicted of treason,

15:11.550 --> 15:13.080
losing all righteousness.

15:14.000 --> 15:15.790
It is not suitable for us
to also turn against him.

15:15.790 --> 15:17.600
If we offend again,

15:18.230 --> 15:21.290
it is equal to making enemies
of the other eight cities.

15:31.820 --> 15:33.060
This time

15:33.520 --> 15:35.440
wasn't completely fruitless.

15:35.460 --> 15:38.180
At least we figured out
Qi Zheng's background.

15:38.600 --> 15:41.600
Ling'an's strength
is also not to be underestimated.

15:42.670 --> 15:43.950
What a pity.

15:44.510 --> 15:46.150
The offense and defense have switched.

15:46.150 --> 15:48.260
We missed a good opportunity.

15:49.030 --> 15:49.750
Well,

15:51.320 --> 15:52.120
Grandfather,

15:53.120 --> 15:55.040
about the gate commander...

15:59.580 --> 16:01.130
First thing tomorrow morning,

16:01.130 --> 16:02.790
I will go to the mansion again.

16:05.120 --> 16:05.520
But

16:05.550 --> 16:07.920
we don't have a large army
to rely on right now.

16:07.920 --> 16:09.090
As long as the Zheng family is here,

16:09.090 --> 16:11.040
even without an army,

16:11.270 --> 16:13.660
Qi Zheng still has to call me Mayor Zheng.

16:18.600 --> 16:20.240
Liu Mu died unexpectedly,

16:20.240 --> 16:23.210
leaving the position of Jing City's
gate commander vacant.

16:23.210 --> 16:26.290
I intend to appoint a new gate commander

16:27.610 --> 16:29.250
to govern Jing City for me.

16:29.750 --> 16:30.950
My beloved subjects,

16:31.320 --> 16:32.670
who is willing to go?

16:35.150 --> 16:36.750
-I'm willing.
-I'm willing.

16:37.750 --> 16:38.480
Tian Xing?

16:40.150 --> 16:40.760
Good.

16:42.070 --> 16:42.960
In my opinion,

16:43.320 --> 16:44.480
you are both excellent candidates

16:44.480 --> 16:46.360
for Jing City's gate commander position.

16:46.360 --> 16:47.470
Today, I plan

16:47.490 --> 16:48.950
to break with convention.

16:49.040 --> 16:50.240
and have the two of you

16:50.510 --> 16:52.510
serve jointly as the gate commander

16:53.270 --> 16:54.730
to govern Jing City for me.

16:55.910 --> 16:56.670
-Yes.
-Yes.

17:00.310 --> 17:01.420
Your Excellency,

17:01.440 --> 17:03.960
two people jointly serving
as the gate commander

17:03.960 --> 17:05.240
is unheard of

17:05.240 --> 17:06.560
and unprecedented.

17:06.579 --> 17:07.619
This is

17:07.670 --> 17:09.310
against the rules.

17:09.829 --> 17:11.960
The previous commoner selection exam

17:12.109 --> 17:13.510
was also unprecedented.

17:13.810 --> 17:15.440
But didn't the facts prove

17:15.460 --> 17:17.119
that it is not only feasible,

17:17.550 --> 17:19.079
but absolutely necessary?

17:19.410 --> 17:22.109
Extraordinary times
call for extraordinary measures.

17:22.109 --> 17:23.310
My mind is made up.

17:23.660 --> 17:25.990
Fan Yun, Tian Xing,

17:26.550 --> 17:28.800
step forward to receive your appointments.

17:28.800 --> 17:30.510
This is the official seal
of the gate commander.

17:30.510 --> 17:32.550
You two will supervise each other

17:33.200 --> 17:34.860
and exercise power together.

17:35.030 --> 17:35.590
In other words,

17:35.590 --> 17:38.440
only together are you
the gate commander of Jing City.

17:38.440 --> 17:39.170
Understand?

17:40.830 --> 17:41.550
-Yes.
-Yes.

17:54.110 --> 17:57.030
Summon Gao Ran for an audience.

18:02.450 --> 18:03.610
Greetings, Your Excellency.

18:03.610 --> 18:05.720
Gao Ran, I appoint you

18:05.750 --> 18:08.490
as the exclusive military officer
for Fan and Tian.

18:08.490 --> 18:10.850
Your mission is to accompany them
to Jing City

18:10.850 --> 18:12.310
and protect their safety.

18:12.700 --> 18:13.560
Can you do that?

18:15.290 --> 18:17.090
Rest assured, Your Excellency.

18:18.930 --> 18:19.960
These twin swords

18:19.980 --> 18:21.580
are named Ganjiang and Moye.

18:22.280 --> 18:24.990
They were given to Second Brother Qingyuan
by the late governor.

18:24.990 --> 18:26.920
They were forged from the same ore.

18:27.240 --> 18:29.290
Back then, Qingyuan gave Moye

18:29.350 --> 18:30.220
to me.

18:31.090 --> 18:32.620
The other sword, Ganjiang,

18:33.110 --> 18:35.870
has been kept in the mansion
all these years.

18:36.590 --> 18:37.680
Today, I plan

18:37.870 --> 18:39.470
to bestow Ganjiang upon you.

18:40.200 --> 18:41.460
Holding this sword

18:42.640 --> 18:44.500
is like having me there in person.

18:47.560 --> 18:48.720
I will strictly obey

18:49.020 --> 18:50.350
the Governor's orders.

19:01.600 --> 19:04.250
[Taiji Palace]

19:03.720 --> 19:04.600
Great.

19:04.640 --> 19:06.530
You've stolen the spotlight again.

19:06.530 --> 19:08.460
But Jing City is not like Yong City.

19:08.640 --> 19:10.350
If you want to be
the gate commander there,

19:10.350 --> 19:12.820
you'd better improve
your self-defense skills.

19:12.820 --> 19:13.930
Don't worry, Bo.

19:14.010 --> 19:15.980
We will definitely stay safe.

19:16.830 --> 19:17.960
Who cares about you?

19:19.580 --> 19:20.180
Let's go.

19:20.710 --> 19:21.550
Fan Yun,

19:21.820 --> 19:22.880
stay here a moment.

19:23.130 --> 19:24.530
I have a few words for you.

19:25.640 --> 19:26.970
I'll take my leave then.

19:29.880 --> 19:30.880
Your Excellency,

19:31.720 --> 19:32.920
what are your orders?

19:35.510 --> 19:36.570
Congratulations.

19:37.020 --> 19:38.790
You finally got what you wanted.

19:38.790 --> 19:40.390
Thank you, Your Excellency.

19:40.590 --> 19:41.550
I didn't expect

19:41.550 --> 19:43.810
you to come up with
the dual gate commander strategy.

19:43.810 --> 19:44.890
This way,

19:44.920 --> 19:46.380
it not only divides power,

19:46.640 --> 19:48.830
but also puts pressure on those
who want to win over the gate commander

19:48.830 --> 19:50.430
and undermine the Qi family.

19:50.670 --> 19:51.630
Of course.

19:52.550 --> 19:53.810
I've already agreed to

19:54.440 --> 19:56.040
the things you asked me to do.

19:56.640 --> 19:58.160
Then shouldn't you

19:59.350 --> 20:00.880
do something for me too?

20:01.400 --> 20:02.250
Tell me.

20:03.750 --> 20:06.240
I sent you to be
the gate commander of Jing City

20:06.240 --> 20:07.200
because

20:07.200 --> 20:09.000
the situation there is unclear.

20:09.330 --> 20:10.660
I have no one else to use,

20:10.960 --> 20:12.170
so I had no choice

20:12.190 --> 20:14.590
but to send you two
to change the situation.

20:16.350 --> 20:18.480
However, this is not a long-term plan.

20:18.550 --> 20:20.350
Jing City will be stable one day.

20:20.790 --> 20:22.520
At that time, shouldn't you...

20:25.510 --> 20:27.170
Shouldn't you reconsider...

20:27.960 --> 20:29.110
Reconsider...

20:29.960 --> 20:30.960
Reconsider what?

20:31.830 --> 20:33.720
Reconsider the marriage.

20:34.930 --> 20:36.720
What did you say?

20:39.070 --> 20:39.830
Shouldn't you

20:39.830 --> 20:41.290
reconsider the marriage?

20:43.560 --> 20:44.320
This...

20:46.200 --> 20:47.310
Why are you bringing

20:47.310 --> 20:48.640
this up again?

20:49.790 --> 20:50.880
Besides,

20:51.350 --> 20:53.270
that didn't really count as

20:53.790 --> 20:54.650
being married.

20:54.830 --> 20:55.550
I know.

20:56.350 --> 20:57.940
I don't mean to force you.

20:59.870 --> 21:01.060
I just want to say

21:02.400 --> 21:04.480
that you want the people to live in peace

21:04.480 --> 21:05.940
before you start a family.

21:06.960 --> 21:08.030
But in my heart,

21:09.070 --> 21:10.800
I actually just want an answer.

21:11.640 --> 21:12.680
What do you think

21:14.110 --> 21:15.400
about me?

21:16.200 --> 21:17.200
I...

21:19.510 --> 21:22.030
I actually... actually...

21:22.060 --> 21:23.100
You what?

21:23.700 --> 21:25.570
Actually, I haven't...

21:25.600 --> 21:26.680
I still...

21:27.790 --> 21:29.790
Haven't thought it through, right?

21:36.880 --> 21:38.200
Fan Yun,

21:39.070 --> 21:40.670
you really care for the world

21:40.920 --> 21:42.440
and the Nine Cities.

21:43.310 --> 21:44.980
I just think

21:45.000 --> 21:47.680
it's too early to talk about this.

21:48.200 --> 21:49.110
Think about it.

21:49.920 --> 21:52.180
The selection exam trial has just begun.

21:52.240 --> 21:53.030
Besides,

21:53.030 --> 21:55.000
I have to go be the gate commander.

21:55.000 --> 21:56.590
Then after your term
as gate commander ends

21:56.590 --> 21:58.310
and Jing City is stabilized,

21:58.900 --> 22:01.220
could you reconsider

22:01.240 --> 22:02.570
your marriage?

22:03.790 --> 22:04.960
If

22:05.640 --> 22:07.610
everything in Jing City is settled

22:08.590 --> 22:11.160
and everything is on the right track,

22:12.440 --> 22:13.200
then...

22:14.320 --> 22:16.610
Then maybe

22:16.640 --> 22:18.480
when I have free time,

22:18.960 --> 22:19.830
I will...

22:19.830 --> 22:21.490
You sure have a lot of demands.

22:22.260 --> 22:23.060
What?

22:23.560 --> 22:24.470
I can't?

22:26.590 --> 22:27.240
You can.

22:28.000 --> 22:28.660
You should.

22:31.000 --> 22:32.930
Then I'll wait for you to come back.

22:37.720 --> 22:38.720
Raise your hands.

22:41.070 --> 22:42.330
Straighten your back.

22:42.400 --> 22:43.730
Hold on a little longer.

22:44.920 --> 22:45.790
Gao Ran,

22:46.160 --> 22:48.480
learning martial arts isn't something
that happens overnight.

22:48.480 --> 22:49.640
No need to rush.

22:50.160 --> 22:51.010
Fan Yun,

22:51.400 --> 22:52.730
if you're tired, get up and take a break.

22:52.730 --> 22:53.680
No.

22:54.160 --> 22:55.030
She just started.

22:55.030 --> 22:56.280
How can she rest already?

22:56.280 --> 22:57.210
Squat properly.

22:57.720 --> 22:59.590
You don't have to start with the basics.

22:59.590 --> 23:01.160
Just learn some self-defense skills
and that's it.

23:01.160 --> 23:02.310
Come, get up. I'll teach you.

23:02.310 --> 23:03.270
It's okay. I...

23:03.270 --> 23:05.070
If you don't master the basics,

23:05.100 --> 23:07.300
what's the use of learning a few tricks?

23:07.400 --> 23:08.070
With me here,

23:08.070 --> 23:09.240
who dares to bully her?

23:09.240 --> 23:10.240
Fan Yun is going to Jing City.

23:10.240 --> 23:10.960
Are you going?

23:10.960 --> 23:11.400
I...

23:11.400 --> 23:12.400
All right, all right,

23:12.400 --> 23:13.860
Both of you, stop arguing.

23:16.200 --> 23:17.480
I just wanted Gao Ran

23:17.480 --> 23:19.740
to teach me a few moves for self-defense.

23:20.240 --> 23:20.920
Your Excellency,

23:20.920 --> 23:22.650
why did you suddenly come here?

23:23.510 --> 23:24.480
Me?

23:25.240 --> 23:26.830
I'm here for a reason, of course.

23:26.830 --> 23:27.750
What reason?

23:30.510 --> 23:31.880
I have something to discuss with Gao Ran.

23:31.880 --> 23:33.140
You take a break first.

23:38.240 --> 23:39.440
You're looking for Gao Ran?

23:39.440 --> 23:41.220
Alright, you guys talk.

23:41.590 --> 23:43.250
I'll go back and get some rest.

23:44.550 --> 23:45.390
Take your time.

23:45.390 --> 23:46.850
-Drink more water.
-Okay.

23:50.780 --> 23:51.780
Your Excellency.

23:54.480 --> 23:55.310
Gao Ran.

23:55.400 --> 23:56.760
Don't you think that

23:57.000 --> 23:58.860
if Fan Yun goes to Jing City alone,

23:58.920 --> 24:00.450
it won't be smooth sailing?

24:03.090 --> 24:05.420
Your Excellency, please speak your mind.

24:08.550 --> 24:09.880
I want to go with Fan Yun.

24:10.090 --> 24:11.550
You are going to Jing City?

24:12.360 --> 24:13.250
How can that do?

24:13.700 --> 24:16.430
The city cannot be
without its governor for a day.

24:17.480 --> 24:18.680
I have made up my mind.

24:20.110 --> 24:21.710
You will act as the governor.

24:22.790 --> 24:24.200
Why are you saying this again?

24:24.200 --> 24:25.350
I won't do

24:25.350 --> 24:26.550
such a treasonous thing,

24:26.550 --> 24:27.790
I am asking you to do it.

24:27.790 --> 24:29.400
How can it be treasonous?

24:29.400 --> 24:31.270
Besides, it's only temporary.

24:31.270 --> 24:32.310
When I come back,

24:32.310 --> 24:34.030
you will naturally return
the position to me.

24:34.030 --> 24:34.760
Don't worry.

24:35.160 --> 24:36.360
All the consequences

24:36.400 --> 24:37.930
will be my responsibility.

24:37.990 --> 24:39.920
No, this won't work.

24:39.950 --> 24:40.950
Even if I agree,

24:41.000 --> 24:42.750
the ministers won't.

24:43.110 --> 24:44.240
As long as you agree,

24:44.440 --> 24:45.720
I have my ways.

24:47.990 --> 24:49.020
Trust me, okay?

25:06.340 --> 25:07.350
Lord Jiang's masks

25:07.350 --> 25:09.280
truly live up to their reputation.

25:09.440 --> 25:10.680
I dare say the masks
in the Nine Cities

25:10.680 --> 25:11.800
are all here.

25:12.750 --> 25:13.440
Lord Jiang,

25:13.820 --> 25:14.930
don't you feel stuffy

25:14.930 --> 25:16.560
when wearing these masks?

25:17.880 --> 25:19.810
When you wear a mask for a long time,

25:19.900 --> 25:21.360
it becomes like clothing.

25:21.790 --> 25:23.990
I'm more uncomfortable not wearing it.

25:26.120 --> 25:27.510
Your Excellency,

25:28.110 --> 25:29.440
you didn't come here

25:29.440 --> 25:31.370
just to admire these masks, right?

25:33.550 --> 25:34.220
Lord Jiang.

25:34.960 --> 25:36.590
Give me some ideas.

25:36.590 --> 25:38.190
Do you have any good methods?

25:43.110 --> 25:44.450
I advise you

25:44.720 --> 25:46.920
to give up these unrealistic thoughts.

25:47.240 --> 25:47.960
I definitely have

25:47.960 --> 25:49.400
a compelling reason to do this.

25:49.400 --> 25:50.880
Why won't you help me?

25:51.170 --> 25:52.650
Why are you like this?

25:53.830 --> 25:54.490
Never mind.

25:55.240 --> 25:56.570
Since you won't help me,

25:57.480 --> 25:59.330
I can only find another way.

26:01.830 --> 26:02.270
I'm leaving.

26:02.270 --> 26:04.030
The past kings were indeed wise.

26:04.030 --> 26:05.510
They must have anticipated that one day,

26:05.510 --> 26:06.550
there would be a governor in power

26:06.550 --> 26:08.400
that was full of wild thoughts.

26:08.400 --> 26:11.130
That's why they created
the Sacred Rites Bureau.

26:16.890 --> 26:18.330
I knew you cared about me.

26:19.100 --> 26:20.500
Thanks for the reminder.

26:37.580 --> 26:39.720
Teacher Ping, what did you say this was?

26:39.720 --> 26:43.750
Some gold, silver, iron,
and bronze headband?

26:44.720 --> 26:46.070
This item is called

26:46.070 --> 26:49.240
the Silver-Threaded Gold-Edged
Eight-Treasure Headband.

26:47.580 --> 26:49.040
[Manager of Sacred Rites Bureau,
Ping Ruying]

26:55.630 --> 26:57.320
The name sounds impressive,

26:57.440 --> 27:00.750
but its appearance is too ordinary.

27:01.280 --> 27:03.350
How can you talk to
Teacher Ping like that?

27:03.350 --> 27:04.680
You call this ordinary?

27:05.160 --> 27:07.070
It's practically an eyesore.

27:07.960 --> 27:09.510
Teacher Ping, are you joking?

27:09.510 --> 27:10.440
Just relying on this thing

27:10.440 --> 27:12.570
can let Gao Ran and me swap identities?

27:13.680 --> 27:16.110
This item is imbued with a spell

27:16.830 --> 27:18.350
that can confuse the mind

27:19.400 --> 27:20.600
and deceive the eyes.

27:21.640 --> 27:22.720
If you put it on,

27:23.270 --> 27:24.750
in the eyes of others,

27:24.750 --> 27:26.680
you will take on each other's appearance.

27:26.680 --> 27:27.400
Moreover,

27:27.400 --> 27:29.400
it won't interfere with each other.

27:32.400 --> 27:33.400
In other words,

27:33.720 --> 27:35.510
if one person takes it off,

27:35.510 --> 27:37.770
it won't affect the other's appearance.

27:38.070 --> 27:38.790
Yes.

27:39.440 --> 27:41.110
What if someone else wears it?

27:41.960 --> 27:44.020
This item is exclusively for you two.

27:44.510 --> 27:45.910
If anyone else puts it on,

27:46.590 --> 27:49.010
it will just turn into a hideous,

27:49.030 --> 27:50.160
ordinary headband.

27:56.690 --> 27:58.230
Is it really that magical?

27:59.880 --> 28:02.210
You can try it on and see,
Your Excellency.

28:26.550 --> 28:27.710
This is too scary.

28:28.350 --> 28:29.310
Gao... Gao Ran, you...

28:29.310 --> 28:30.570
You've turned into me.

28:30.720 --> 28:32.070
Th-This is amazing.

28:36.960 --> 28:38.070
Teacher Ping,

28:38.510 --> 28:40.310
this is indeed a great treasure.

28:40.550 --> 28:42.790
This is exactly what I wanted.

29:06.310 --> 29:07.470
Shi.

29:19.400 --> 29:20.470
Grandfather?

29:27.900 --> 29:28.600
Sit.

29:33.780 --> 29:34.900
Grandfather,

29:36.240 --> 29:37.350
you're back?

29:40.240 --> 29:42.550
I was worried,

29:44.830 --> 29:46.310
so I came to see you.

29:53.190 --> 29:54.520
I've been watching you

29:56.480 --> 29:58.360
for a long time.

30:07.910 --> 30:09.640
I'll leave after taking a look.

30:29.480 --> 30:31.310
I know what you care about.

30:32.240 --> 30:33.160
Don't worry,

30:33.680 --> 30:35.740
I will definitely achieve it for you.

30:58.130 --> 30:59.370
Then what about

31:00.480 --> 31:04.040
the things you deeply desired?

31:08.660 --> 31:10.130
♪ I could have ♪

31:10.160 --> 31:11.760
♪ Played every trick in the book ♪

31:11.780 --> 31:15.140
♪ But I chose painstaking devotion ♪

31:12.480 --> 31:13.810
I don't want it anymore.

31:15.320 --> 31:16.980
♪ Never caging my love ♪

31:17.000 --> 31:21.230
♪ Even if I had to
trudge through a thousand miles ♪

31:19.510 --> 31:20.970
I don't want them anymore.

31:21.350 --> 31:25.430
♪ Henceforth, I shall wander the world,
plucking petals and holding the moon ♪

31:25.690 --> 31:29.000
♪ Listen to the wind and admire the moon
for days on end ♪

31:28.960 --> 31:30.130
Where are you going?

31:29.180 --> 31:35.100
♪ Accept that I'm not your happiness ♪

31:35.180 --> 31:37.890
♪ Let go of what's before me ♪

31:37.920 --> 31:41.880
♪ Consider this the best ending ♪

31:41.790 --> 31:43.030
Grandfather, don't go.

31:41.990 --> 31:44.480
♪ I disdain everything
in the vast universe ♪

31:44.500 --> 31:48.860
♪ So why do I care for
a single glance from you? ♪

31:46.720 --> 31:48.070
Grandfather, don't go!

31:48.880 --> 31:51.520
♪ Drinking a pot of the past ♪

31:49.030 --> 31:50.110
Grandfather!

31:51.540 --> 31:56.390
♪ I toast to my withering self
as the curtains fall ♪

31:56.420 --> 32:02.640
♪ And you don't know the reason why ♪

31:56.920 --> 31:58.810
My grandson, Shi,

32:01.650 --> 32:03.490
just go

32:05.440 --> 32:07.480
and live the free life

32:09.030 --> 32:11.300
you want.

32:09.350 --> 32:12.060
♪ Let go of what's before me ♪

32:12.080 --> 32:16.040
♪ Consider this the best ending ♪

32:16.330 --> 32:18.810
♪ I disdain everything
in the vast universe ♪

32:18.590 --> 32:20.400
Let me

32:18.840 --> 32:23.200
♪ So why do I care for
a single glance from you? ♪

32:22.200 --> 32:24.270
bear those responsibilities

32:23.220 --> 32:25.850
♪ Drinking a pot of the past ♪

32:25.880 --> 32:30.730
♪ I toast to my withering self
as the curtains fall ♪

32:26.000 --> 32:29.720
alone.

32:30.770 --> 32:37.000
♪ And you don't know the reason why ♪

32:37.840 --> 32:44.070
♪ And you don't know the reason why ♪

32:48.060 --> 32:49.820
I prepared this meal today

32:50.530 --> 32:52.050
to say goodbye to you.

32:53.400 --> 32:54.480
Say goodbye?

32:55.790 --> 32:57.320
Second Young Master Zheng,

32:57.480 --> 32:58.610
where are you going?

33:00.070 --> 33:01.810
I need to take my grandfather's ashes

33:01.810 --> 33:04.030
back to Jing City for burial
as soon as possible.

33:04.030 --> 33:06.690
From now on,
I have no relatives left in Ling'an,

33:07.440 --> 33:08.900
so I have no reason to stay.

33:11.070 --> 33:11.800
I don't know

33:13.310 --> 33:15.310
when we will see each other again.

33:17.400 --> 33:18.600
You're talking as if

33:19.200 --> 33:20.960
we are parting forever.

33:22.240 --> 33:24.370
Why don't you come with me to Jing City?

33:29.160 --> 33:29.960
Sure.

33:30.960 --> 33:32.360
Then see you in Jing City.

33:35.110 --> 33:35.880
Then,

33:36.080 --> 33:36.950
I...

33:36.980 --> 33:38.780
I'll go prepare a nice carriage.

33:40.710 --> 33:41.820
Second Young Master Zheng,

33:41.820 --> 33:43.090
actually, the governor

33:43.090 --> 33:45.580
appointed me as the gate commander
of Jing City.

33:45.580 --> 33:46.540
This time,

33:46.570 --> 33:48.430
I'll be going with the main force.

33:51.920 --> 33:53.360
Being the gate commander of Jing City

33:53.360 --> 33:54.710
is very dangerous.

33:54.960 --> 33:56.440
But since you've decided,

33:56.680 --> 33:57.880
I will do my best

33:57.880 --> 33:59.880
to help you be a good gate commander.

34:00.190 --> 34:01.230
Help me?

34:04.400 --> 34:05.720
Zheng Tao

34:05.720 --> 34:07.120
brought an army this time

34:07.270 --> 34:10.270
to help Zheng Xian
get the position of gate commander,

34:10.730 --> 34:12.460
but he returned disappointed.

34:13.000 --> 34:14.730
As a member of the Zheng family,

34:14.880 --> 34:17.340
are you sure you want to help me,
an outsider?

34:17.880 --> 34:19.840
If someone else
were to be the gate commander,

34:19.840 --> 34:21.300
I would naturally object.

34:21.550 --> 34:22.940
But if it's you,

34:23.480 --> 34:24.940
that's a different story.

34:26.190 --> 34:27.070
Why?

34:28.400 --> 34:30.000
You be the gate commander of Jing City,

34:30.000 --> 34:31.630
and I'll be the Master
of the Zheng family.

34:31.630 --> 34:33.889
Is there a better arrangement than this?

34:35.480 --> 34:36.920
You want to be the Master?

34:37.239 --> 34:38.280
Why not?
